  "title": "URGENT START⚡️- Sales Associate (traveling opportunities/office hours))",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚀 What You Need to do:</strong></p>\n<p>🎯 Deliver captivating in-person presentations on both B2C and B2B platforms</p>\n<p>🧠 Develop, implement, and oversee sales and marketing plans to assist the group in reaching goals.</p>\n<p>Identify what the customers want and offer the best goods and services.</p>\n<p>✅ Provide clear, understandable information and a transparent and open sales process.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>👀<strong> You have what we are looking for:</strong></p>\n<p>📚 An active student mentality, always eager to learn and grow with the company</p>\n<p>💪 Strong determination and mindset to overcome hurdles to succeed.</p>\n<p>🌀 Adaptable and able to keep up in a fast-paced environment</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🎁 Your benefits &amp; opportunities:</strong></p>\n<p>📈 Guided and laid out growth plans based on your performance</p>\n<p>🎉 Working in a family &amp; friends like environment</p>\n<p>🧑‍🏫 Mentorship provided—0 experience will be trained by experienced</p>\n<p>✈️ Get your passport ready to travel with us internationally</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>💡 Get ready to start right now!</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Nothing is more expensive than a missed opportunity! </strong></p>\n<p><strong>click APPLY NOW!</strong></p>",
